cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.CY

The paper analyzes the dynamic usage history of scientific literature, which involves the study of digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The focus is on the usage of Nature publications, which are related to cryptography (cs.CR), social and information networks (cs.SI), and cybernetics (cs.CY).
